<db:para>The <db:link xlink:href="http://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/ASIN/0735605661/trolltech/t">Microsoft book</db:link> has ISBN 0735605661. The corresponding Open Group book is very hard to find, rather expensive and we cannot recommend it. However, if you really want it, ogpubs@opengroup.org might be able to help. Ask them for ISBN 1859121047.</db:para>
